      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Why is Costco hot dog only $1.50?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Costco keeps the hot dog at $1.50 as a loss leader to attract members to the warehouse. The company absorbs the cost to maintain customer loyalty and foot traffic.</p>
      </div>
